The paper discusses the development of computer-assisted diagnosis of lung nodules using image analysis techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also extensively discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which are a subset of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the challenges and opportunities for future work in this field, which may involve information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques for data analysis and management.
